                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-58-defend552 t18110403-58-punish344"></join>
               Confined Two Years in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18110403-58-punish345" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18110403-58-punish345" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18110403-58-punish345" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-58-defend552 t18110403-58-punish345"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>NEALE, <rs id="t18110403-58-verdict346" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18110403-58-verdict346" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 27.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18110403-58-punish347" type="punishmentDescription">
