                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110403-58-defend554 t18110403-58-punish347"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. justice Chambre.</p>
            </div1>
